data.description: Looking for a Ranchette on the Central Coast? Would you like to build that workshop that you've always dreamed of or maybe a guest house for Mom and Dad? There is plenty of room to do that and more on this fully usable acre in Nipomo. Only minutes from the Pacific Ocean, Nipomo is known for its great climate! Call today to visit this wonderful brand new single level home with modern designer touches throughout. The moment you enter this home, you will be captivated by the soaring ceilings and open floorplan. Gourmet kitchen has a large island, lots of cabinets, stainless appliances, walk-in pantry, quartz counters and plenty of room for the family to gather or to entertain. There are two luxurious master bedrooms with large walk-in closets! The main master suite has a huge soaking tub and with a large separate shower. You will love the 3 patios which you can access from the living room and each master bedroom. Builder will give a $5,000 landscape allowance! This property is all level and only minutes to the beach. Call Nancy today!
